---
title: "MCP Tool Wiring - How Agents Connect to Services"
---
graph LR
    subgraph AGENTS["LangGraph Agents - MCP Clients"]
        ROUTER["Router\n(Haiku)"]
        COACH["Coach\n(Claude Sonnet)"]
        ASSISTANT["Assistant\n(Gemini)"]
    end

    subgraph MCP_SERVERS["MCP Servers - Standalone Processes"]
        HS["HubSpot MCP Server\nOfficial Public Beta\n+ shinzo-labs/hubspot-mcp\n\nRead: contacts, companies,\ndeals, tickets, notes\nWrite: create/update deals,\ncontacts, log activities\nAuth: OAuth 2.0"]

        BQ["BigQuery MCP Server\nGoogle Official Managed\n\nQuery: Run SQL\nSchema: Inspect tables\nAuth: Service Account"]

        GM["Gmail MCP Server\nshinzo-labs/gmail-mcp\nor GongRzhe/Gmail-MCP\n\nRead: search, get messages\nWrite: create drafts, send\nAuth: OAuth 2.0 via Google"]

        WS["Web Search MCP\nTavily MCP Server\n\nSearch: web queries\nExtract: page content\nAuth: API key"]

        VDB["Vector DB MCP\nCustom wrapper\n\nSearch: semantic + keyword\nIndex: add/update docs\nTarget: Qdrant or Weaviate"]
    end

    COACH ---|MCP Protocol| HS
    COACH ---|MCP Protocol| BQ
    COACH ---|MCP Protocol| WS
    COACH ---|MCP Protocol| VDB
    ASSISTANT ---|MCP Protocol| HS
    ASSISTANT ---|MCP Protocol| BQ
    ASSISTANT ---|MCP Protocol| GM
    ASSISTANT ---|MCP Protocol| WS
